</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>The Prince</SPEAKER>
<P><STAGE>(<HI>taking his hand.</HI>)</STAGE>
Good-hearted little f<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">llow! you have <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">rificed, then, the &s;ole object of your own wi&s;hes, to give &s;uccour to your mother? It would be barbarous to &s;uffer an action, &s;uch as that, to deprive you of your watch. Here
<STAGE>(<HI>holding to him his own</HI>)</STAGE>
