</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>The Page</SPEAKER>
<P><STAGE>(<HI>a&s;toni&s;hed.</HI>)</STAGE>
What, Sir!</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>The Prince.</SPEAKER>
<P>Do you he&s;itate? Take it, I tell you.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>The Page.</SPEAKER>
<P>What! the pur&s;e, and all that is in it too? O no! it's too much,
