</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>The Prince.</SPEAKER>
<P>Certainly too much, were it all de&s;igned for your&s;elf: but I only put it into your hands to di&s;po&s;e of it. And who can you think of, that might find it mo&s;t u&s;eful?</P>
</SP>
<SP>
